      Token TokenInputStream.actual()

      Only use, if you need a complete Token. Use TokenInputStream.actualType(), TokenInputStream.actualStart(), TokenInputStream.actualEnd(), TokenInputStream.actualValue() & TokenInputStream.actualHasValue() instead, if you just need one of these!

      Deprecated. 
      Token[] TokenInputStream.getTokens()
      Getter for TokenInputStream.tokens (Gives back an array of Tokens)
      Token TokenInputStream.next()
      Deprecated.

      Token TokenInputStream.peek()
      Deprecated. 
      Only use, if you need a complete Token. Use TokenInputStream.peekType(), TokenInputStream.peekStart(), TokenInputStream.peekEnd(), TokenInputStream.peekValue() & TokenInputStream.peekHasValue() instead, if you just need one of these!
